==Trivia==
*Mammoths were originally a cut race in ''RuneScape 2''. A [[Update:Upcoming RuneScape updates|Behind the Scenes]] article from March 2004 promised that one of the upcoming updates would be ''"A large 'frozen lands' area including penguins, mammoths, polar bears and more."''. The original version of Mammoths remained in the game files long after the Wilderness Mammoths were added, only being removed in 2017 when Mammoths became a Slayer task.
*Mammoths first made their appearance at an exhibit in [[Prifddinas]] during ''Old School RuneScape's'' [[2014 Birthday event|first anniversary]]. They were added to the [[Wilderness]] with the [[Update:Rejuvenating the Wilderness: More risk, more reward|Wilderness Rejuvenation update]] of [[13 March]] [[2014]].
*Mammoths are referred to as 'elephantine' in their examine texts despite no elephants existing in Gielinor for them to resemble.
*Mammoths have had a [[:File:Mammoth_(Christmas).png|festive override]] wearing the [[wise old man's santa hat]] during every [[Christmas event]] since [[2018 Christmas event|2018]].

